20unlike%20the%20legacy%20Hollywood%20model.%20Apart%20from%20a%20short-lived%20experiment%20in%20funding%20its%20own%20shows%2C%20it's%20stuck%20with%20supporting%20creators%20with%20tools%20like%20automatic%20dubbing%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Fnews-and-events%2Fmade-on-youtube-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETV-like%20interface%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20promote%20binge-watching%2C%20and%20features%20that%20let%20creators%20comment%20on%20and%20react%20to%20live%20events.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20it%20typically%20shares%2055%25%20of%20the%20revenue%20from%20ads%20shown%20on%20creators'%20videos.%20YouTube%20execs%20often%20tout%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fcreators%2Fpartner-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2470%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20paid%20to%20creators%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20media%20companies%20over%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20has%20had%20limited%20success%20attracting%20blue-chip%20advertisers%20who%20have%20a%20bias%20for%20TV-like%20shows%2C%20though%2C%20something%20top%20creators%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhot-ones-sean-evans-criticizes-advertisers-undervaluing-youtube-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESean%20Evans%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20complained%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20latest%20advertiser%20pitch%20hopes%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20of%20what%20YouTube%20hopes%20will%20be%20many%20examples%2C%20State%20Farm%20owned%20the%20recent%20PGA%20Championship%20on%20YouTube.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20ran%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eads%20on%20trending%20videos%2C%20takeovers%20on%20golf%20channels%20from%20creators%20like%20Grant%20Horvat%20and%20Good%20Good%2C%20and%20an%20integration%20into%20the%20new%20LOL%20Network%20series%20%26quot%3BCaddie%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Kid%26quot%3B%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcele