fintech%20company%20provides%20cross-border%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-management-startup-plum-adds-stock-trading-airwallex-partnership-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epayments%20and%20financial%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20its%20banking%20network%20and%20protocols%20that%20allow%20different%20software%20components%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20that%20it%20raised%20%24300%20million%20in%20a%20series%20F%20funding%20round%20at%20a%20valuation%20of%20%246.2%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20said%20that%20his%20second%20mistake%20was%20that%20Airwallex%20overinvested%20in%20international%20expansion%20without%20having%20a%20product-market%20fit.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20got%20lucky%2C%20but%20doing%20this%20carried%20a%20lot%20of%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20the%20last%20thing%20he%20would%20change%20would%20be%20investing%20in%20company%20culture%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20early%20first%20four%2C%20five%20years%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20from%20a%20bank%2C%20they're%20from%20Citibank%2C%20they've%20built%20a%20Swift%20network%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20join%2C%20they're%20telling%20you%2C%20'you%20guys%20know%20nothing%2C%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20doesn't%20work.'%20None%20of%20those%20people%20worked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20experience%20matters%20less%20than%20other%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20just%20have%20hired%20those%20curious%2C%20determined%2C%20optimistic%20people%20from%20early%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20didn't%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20fire%20all%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20speaking%20of%20his%20challenging%20early%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20is%20among%20tech%20CEOs%20who%20hav