t%3B%20at%20Harvard%20amid%20the%20American%20university's%20ongoing%20conflict%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhong-kong-invites-top-talent-amid-trumps-international-student-ban-on-harvard-8517857%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20CEO%20of%20a%20%246%20billion%20fintech%20explains%20how%20the%20huge%20risk%20he%20took%20with%20thousands%20of%20banks%20paid%20off%20big%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224058%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zach%20Perret%2C%20CEO%20of%20Plaid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683542cec6ad288d1481e85b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlaid's%20CEO%2C%20Zach%20Perret%2C%20said%20the%20company%20scraped%20data%20from%2012%2C000%20banks.%3Cp%3ECody%20Glenn%2FSportsfile%20for%20Web%20Summit%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPlaid's%20CEO%20said%20the%20company%20made%20a%20risky%20gamble%20in%20its%20early%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPlaid%20pulled%20user%20data%20from%2012%2C000%20banks%20using%20screen%20scraping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20the%20company's%20early%20work%20with%20banks%20was%20%26quot%3Bantagonistic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zach%20Perret.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaid-identity-verification-information-sharing-plans-growth-strategy-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efintech%20company%20Plaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20an%20essential%20link%20between%20banks%20and%20digital%20finance%20apps%20like%20Venmo%2C%20Robinhood%2C%20and%20Coinbase%2C%20its%20founders%20made%20a%20risky%20gamble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202013%2C%20Plaid's%20leaders%20recognized%20a%20gap.%20While%20consumers%20had%20the%20right%20to%20access%20their%20financial%20data%2C%20banks%20didn't%20have%20official%20application%20program%20interfaces%20for%20companies%20like%20Plaid%20to%20access%20the%20data%20on%20behalf%20of%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20in%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPlaid%20relied%20on%20a%20practice%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bscreen%20scraping%2C%26quot%3B%20essentially%20logging%20into%20users'%20bank%20accounts%20with%20their%20usernames%20and%20passwords%20to%20retrieve%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScreen%20scraping%20can%20raise%20privacy%20and%20security%20concerns%20because%20it%20requires%20sharing%20sensitive%20login%20credentials%20and%20bypasses%20banks'%20direct%20control%20over%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAcquired%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20Tuesday%2C%20Plaid's%20CEO%2C%20Zach%20Perret%2C%20said%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompany%20scraped%20data%20from%2012%2C000%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoing%20this%20at%20scale%20is%20very%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20Perret%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20some%20of%20Plaid's%20work%20with%20banks%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20collaborative%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20other%20work%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20more%20antagonistic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20banks%20were%20frustrated%20that%20investing%20apps%20like%20Robinhood%20even%20existed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20resistance%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20Plaid%20to%20work%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBroadly%2C%20our%20goal%20was%20always%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20banks%20actually%20came%20to%20us%20and%20said%2C%20'Great%2C%20we'd%20like%20to%20move%20to%20an%20API.%20We%20haven't%20built%20it%20yet.%20Please%20just%20screen%20scrape%20us%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Plaid%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%2458%20million%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaid-class-action-privacy-lawsuit-settlement-58-million-data-aggregator-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esettle%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20data%20privacy.%20The%20case%2C%20filed%20in%20California%2C%20consolidated%20five%20lawsuits%20brought%20by%20consumers%20who%20said%20Plaid%20accessed%20their%20bank%20account%20data%20without%20their%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20also%20said%20that%20Plaid%20sold%20user%20data%20%E2%80%94%20a%20claim%20the%20company%20has%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Plaid%20publicly%20committed%20to%20moving%2075%25%20of%20its%20data%20volumes%20to%20APIs%2C%20not%20screen%20scraping%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20we%20have%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20our%20data%20coming%20from%20API-driven%20integrations%2C%26quot%3B%20Perret%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20adding%20that%20banks%20have%20built%20their%20own%20APIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlaid%20is%20now%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20long-term%20sustainable%20technical%20infrastructure%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerret%20said%20that%20he%20was%20initially%20skeptical%20about%20whether%20people%20would%20want%20to%20link%20their%20bank%20accounts%20to%20apps%20like%20Venmo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20turns%20out%20people%20did%20it%20in%20droves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20chicken%20and%20egg%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Perret%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20build%20the%20less%20scalable%20integrations%20before%20we%20could%20get%20to%20the%20more%20scalable%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Plaid%20raised%20%24575%20million%20at%20a%20%246.1%20billion%20valuation%2C%20in%20a%20round%20led%20by%20Franklin%20Templeton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerret%20and%20Plaid%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2