dia.com%2F432674%2Fwildlife-photographer-sanket-reddy-lessons-nature%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuit%20of%20wildlife%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Intrigued%2C%20I%20added%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20ancient%20citadel%20to%20my%20itinerary%2C%20little%20knowing%20the%20profound%20connection%20I%20would%20feel%20to%20this%20historical%20and%20spiritual%20heart%20of%20Ranthambore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EClimbing%20into%20the%20past%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20morning%2C%20I%20surprised%20myself.%20I%20altered%20my%20itinerary%2C%20postponing%20the%20safari%20and%20deciding%20to%20begin%20the%20day%20with%20a%20climb%20to%20Ranthambore%20Fort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20fort%2C%20the%20sun%20was%20still%20mellow%2C%20casting%20a%20soft%20glow%20on%20the%20Aravalli%20hills.%20The%20air%20was%20cooler%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20touched%20by%20the%20forest%20dew.%20The%20path%20ahead%2C%20with%20stone%20steps%20winding%20upward%20through%20ancient%20gates%2C%20looked%20less%20like%20a%20tourist%20trail%20and%20more%20like%20an%20entry%20into%20time%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20climb%20was%20steep%20in%20parts%2C%20slow%20in%20others%2C%20but%20never%20dull.%20With%20each%20turn%2C%20the%20forest%20below%20opened%20up%20in%20grander%20sweeps.%20I%20paused%20often%2C%20not%20from%20fatigue%20but%20from%20awe.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20reached%20the%20top%2C%20the%20jungle%20had%20fallen%20into%20a%20soft%20hush%20behind%20me%2C%20and%20in%20front%20of%20me%20lay%20the%20vast%20sprawl%20of%20Ranthambore%20Fort%20with%20its%20sandstone%20ramparts%2C%20weathered%20but%20still%20proud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp